{
  "texts": [
    "Their objective is to bolster the security of patient data in response to advancing technology.",
    "• Technological Integration: Both studies include stateof-the-art technology in their frameworks.",
    "SSEHCET utilizes IoT, 5G, mobile edge computing, and blockchain technology.",
    "In contrast, Paper [58] integrates deep learning and multi-agent systems to tackle privacy issues.• Security measures: Both SSEHCET and Paper [58] use security measures to guarantee the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of patient data.",
    "SSEHCET does this by using a replicated Smart Agent program, whereas Paper [58] utilizes measures based on many agents for instantaneous assessment."
  ]
}